k=A.xo("Guess the 5-letter word in 6 tries. After each guess, the tiles will change color to show how close you are:\n\n- Green: Letter is correct and in the right position\n- Yellow: Letter is in the word but wrong position\n- Gray: Letter is not in the word",n,q,s,o,"How do I play Classic mode?",p)
